==Trivia==
*Bob's name is a play on [[Wikipedia:Bob Barker|Bob Barker]], the name of the former host of the game show ''[[Wikipedia:The Price is Right|The Price is Right]]'', and the word "barter".
*When asking him for prices on a [[free-to-play]] world, the prices for herbs are listed, but the herbs' names are not displayed - they are all called "[[Members object]]".
*In one go, Bob can decant up to 2,147,483,647 (the maximum number of items allowed in a stack) doses of up to 27 types of potions.
*While decanting potions, Bob may say "''Two plus two is four, minus one that's three...''", a reference to the song "{{wp|Man's Not Hot}}" by Big Shaq.

